trans-unit.source: Represents pre-allocated state for native overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: Representa el estado preasignado para las operaciones de E/S superpuestas nativas.

trans-unit.source: A delegate that represents the callback method to invoke when each asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: Delegado que representa el método de devolución de llamada que se invocará cuando se completen las operaciones de E/S asincrónicas.

trans-unit.source: A user-supplied object that distinguishes the <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instance produced from this object from other <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: Objeto proporcionado por el usuario que distingue la instancia de <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> generada a partir de este objeto desde otras instancias de <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: An object or array of objects that represent the input or output buffer for the operations.
trans-unit.target: Objeto o una matriz de objetos que representan el búfer de entrada o salida para las operaciones.

trans-unit.source: Each object represents a buffer, such as an array of bytes.
trans-unit.target: Cada objeto representa un búfer, como una matriz de bytes.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" /> class and specifies a delegate to invoke when each asynchronous I/O operation is complete, a user-provided object that provides context, and managed objects that serve as buffers.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" /> y especifica un delegado que se va a invocar cuando se completen todas las operaciones de E/S asincrónicas, un objeto proporcionado por el usuario que proporciona contexto y los objetos administrados que actúan como búferes.

trans-unit.source: The new <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instance can be passed to the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped%2A> method to produce a <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> instance that can be passed to the operating system in overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: El nuevo <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instancia puede pasarse a la <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped%2A> método para generar un <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> superpuesta de instancia que se puede pasar al sistema operativo en las operaciones de E/S.

trans-unit.source: A single <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instance can only be used for a single native I/O operation at a time.
trans-unit.target: Una sola <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instancia solo se puede usar para una única operación de E/S de nativo a la vez.

trans-unit.source: However, the state stored in the <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instance can be reused for subsequent native operations.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, el estado se almacena en la <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped> instancia se puede reutilizar para las operaciones posteriores nativo.

trans-unit.source: The buffers specified in `pinData` are pinned until the <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped.Dispose%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Los búferes especificados en `pinData` anclado hasta que el <xref:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped.Dispose%2A> se llama al método.

trans-unit.source: This method was called after the <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> was disposed.
trans-unit.target: Se llamó a este método después de eliminar <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" />.

trans-unit.source: Frees the resources associated with this <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Libera los recursos asociados a esta instancia de <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: Frees unmanaged resources before the current instance is reclaimed by garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Libera recursos no administrados antes de que la colección de elementos reclame la instancia actual.
